


x_choose(1)                    Scilab Function                    x_choose(1)






NAME
  x_choose - interactive Xwindow choice

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [num]=x_choose(items,title)

PARAMETERS

  items
       : column vector of string,  items to choose

  title
       : column vector of string, comment for the dialog

  num  : integer, choosen item number or 0 if dialog resumed with "Cancel"
       button

DESCRIPTION
  Returns in num the number of the chosen item.

EXAMPLE
  n=x_choose(['item1';'item2';'item3'],['that is a comment';'for the dialog'])


































